OL,5, Forcing councillors in England to      
OL,6, attend meetings in person is leading to
OL,7, some quitting, councils have warned.   
OL,9,FA legal requirement to hold full       
OL,10,Fcouncil meetings in person was         
OL,11,Ftemporarily dropped during the pandemic
OL,12,Fbut reintroduced in May 2021.          
OL,14,FA survey by the Local Government       
OL,15,FAssociation (LGA) found one in 10      
OL,16,Fcouncils had seen members stand down   
OL,17,Fsince then due to the change.          
OL,19,FThe government said in-person meetings 
OL,20,Fwere important for accountability.     
